data.description: Welcome to 13626 Paseo Del Mar! This 3 bedroom, 2 bath home invites you from the moment you step through the double doors to the completely redone yard! From the entry you will feel the are welcomed by the living room with large window and fireplace, creating a cozy ambiance for relaxation and entertainment.The floor plan provides seamless transitions between living spaces and outdoor features. Discover a host of upgrades, including a PAID solar panels, newer electrical panel, and complete HVAC system and  ensuring a comfortable and efficient living environment. Enjoy a completely redone backyard with turf, vinyl fencing that boasts a pet enclosure, offering a perfect blend of outdoor enjoyment and pet-friendly living- as well as side parking for RV? TOYS? Say goodbye to the hassle of constant maintenance, as this property is designed for ease .The great location of this property delivers the perfect balance of tranquility and accessibility, with close proximity to the 8 freeway for easy commuting while the functionality welcomes you home!
